---
import ProjectLayout from "../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
import Image from "../components/Image.astro";
import Video from "../components/Video.astro";
---

<style>
    .three-column-text {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: var(--space-8);
        margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    }

    .three-column-text p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: var(--font-size-base);
        line-height: var(--line-height-normal);
        font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
        color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .mockup-images {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .three-column-text .end-column {
        grid-column: 3;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .three-column-text {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: var(--space-6);
        }
        
        .three-column-text .end-column {
            grid-column: 1;
        }
    }
</style>

<ProjectLayout
    title="Khthon"
    subtitle="Web design | Brand identity"
    description="Developing the website and brand identity of an open source intelligence research company"
>

    <Video
        src="../videos/khthon-mockup-homepage-scroll-optimized.mp4"
        srcMobile="../videos/khthon-mockup-homepage-scroll-mobile.mp4"
        poster="../images/khthon-mockup-homepage-scroll-poster.webp"
        size="full"
        autoplay={true}
        loop={true}
        controls={false}
        muted={true}
    />

    <div class="three-column-text">
        <p>Khthon was looking to achieve a more consistent and professional look. What started with a website redesign soon grew into a whole rebrand that meant rethinking the organisation's visual identity.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="three-column-text">
        <p>Working together with the marketing, HR and operations, GIS, and research teams, we created a visual language balancing seriousness, flexibility, and aesthetics.</p>
    </div>

    <Video
        src="../videos/thumbnail-images-collage-video-optimized.mp4"
        srcMobile="../videos/thumbnail-images-collage-video-mobile.mp4"
        poster="../images/khthon-mockup-homepage-scroll-poster.webp"
        size="large"
        autoplay={true}
        loop={true}
        controls={false}
        muted={true}
    />

    <div class="three-column-text">
        <p class="end-column">The redesign achieved consistency across all the organisation's channels and production, and streamlined the creation of social media, research and web content. Traffic to the website has since increased by 50% and maintained engagement with the research.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mockup-images">
        <Image
            src="../images/khthon-mockup-2.webp"
            alt="Mockup of Khthon's website shoing on a laptop on a white background"
        />
            
        <Image
            src="../images/khthon-report-components.webp"
            alt="Screenshot of wireframe components used for the website designs"
        />
    </div>

    <div class="three-column-text">
        <p>As the organisation is run by volunteers, there were challenges like intermittent communication, and constant team turnover that required adaptability and flexibility. The most significant learning opportunity came from advocating for UX design's strategic value, educating stakeholders, establishing evidence-based decision-making processes, and positioning design expertise as integral to the organisation.</p>
    </div>

</ProjectLayout>